### GET /api/flights | Recuperar todos los vuelos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flights

### GET /api/flights/origin/:origin | Recuperar vuelos por origen
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flights/origin/Barcelona

### POST /api/flights/:id | Crear un vuelo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "flight_number": "1234",
    "origin": "Barcelona",
    "destination": "Lisbon",
    "departure_date": "2026-01-20 12:00:00",
    "arrival_date": "2026-01-20 15:00:00",
    "price": 247.00,
    "cancelled": false,
    "airline_id": 1
}

### PUT /api/flights/:id | Actualizar un vuelo
